Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  今天我必須得去社團一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯也有了能夠熱衷去做的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知是該高興還是難過…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天紬紬要帶來很好吃的點心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是彈吉他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是幼稚園
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是國小
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使成了國中生  也還一直過著無所事事的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但成為高中生的我第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加社團了！
